2. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the problem of computing a function of a sequence available only at the encoder and a sequence that can be measured only at the decoder, which is a problem in control systems. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the problem of encoding a sequence, which is a problem in multimedia. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper deals with the problem of optimizing a cost function, which is a problem in machine learning. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper deals with the problem of designing an optimal system, which is a problem in data structures and algorithms.
